### GUARDRAIL (single check)

Before producing logic, confirm the alert contains no indicators that contradict filterability: confirmed-malicious IOC (VT hits in an enrichment block, known malware family), active C2, credential dumping, lateral movement, or hands-on-keyboard activity. If any are present, do NOT generate a filter. Output one line: `Filter not advised — alert contains [indicator]. Confirm disposition before suppression.` and stop.

